        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Stop Sanctions Violators Act </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the President from modifying civil penalties as applied to a Chinese telecommunications firm for violations of export controls or sanctions laws unless certain requirements are met. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
